{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- so the first transport went-- went out on-- on-- on May-- let's say May 19, 1944.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a sight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I saw the people in the first transport, people-- and men, women, and children everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I come from a very religious home and I was only a young boy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, there is no God.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To see a sight like this-- you can read as many books as you want.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is unbelievable, to see a site like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Little was I to realize that I'm going to be in the same-- same group, only a week later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it's different when you're in it, or when you see it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Somehow when you're in it, you don't-- it doesn't have that-- that impact like seeing it the first time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't know where they were going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The were taken-- they were taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As soon as they were taken out, a third of the ghetto was empty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I went into that third and I found some very nice suits with shirts and everything because people left it behind.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I dressed up like a millionaire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I looked like a rich man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] For the first time I felt like I am rich because they had all kinds of food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They left a lot of stuff behind in the-- in the third section.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A week later, on a Friday, it was, I think, May 26, it was-- exactly end of-- no, it was shul was Sunday and Monday, and this was just the Friday before shul.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Our turn came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Again, I was part of the same mass of people, the second section.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then I know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They took us to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they took away, again, if they found anything left on us, they took it away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there already they were looking brutal, because there was one incident [SIGHING] where they kept-- there were Germans there already.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, go fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And for some reason I, like, I got a little bit lost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this Nazi he hit me with, like with a baseball bat on my-- on my back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he sort of knocked the wind out of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I couldn't breathe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my mother was behind me and she gave me a push.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I looked back and I saw my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I-- I saw-- I saw-- I know I saw her face.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She was helpless.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it's another sight which is very hard for me to--to forget.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so we were pushed along and we were taken out to the railroad station, in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And over there there were wagons, cattle cars, waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they started to load them up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "As people came, they started to load up car number one, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And in every car where I went in there was like a couple of loaves of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And there was a pail of water-- fresh, I mean water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And one pail was like for sanitary purposes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we were jammed into that-- you-- you-- you people couldn't lay down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I want you to know that my great grandmother, my great grandmother, that I told you before, she was in the same transport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "When she came to the ghetto the only thing she took along was her [NON-ENGLISH], because she made her own [NON-ENGLISH]-- her own [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And this is the only thing she held on to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Even when they took us out to the train, she held onto this bundle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "In case she died, she wanted to be buried in the [NON-ENGLISH], in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they-- people were dying in the train, too, because there was no room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It was-- everybody was jammed in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And there were fights breaking out-- people didn't get along.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Because, you know, to stay crammed up like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Every-- [SIGHS] And then they closed the doors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They closed the doors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "There were two sliding doors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Or one sliding door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They closed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And in the top there was a little window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "The window must have been maybe about-- about maybe 12, 14 inches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Maybe about 20 inches or 2 feet long by 12, 14 inches high.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And under the window there was barbed wire, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I was near the window and I would sometimes pull myself up and look out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "You know, I could look out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we left [NON-ENGLISH], that-- I would say, around 1 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And we arrived midnight to a place called Kosice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Kosice, this is what it's called in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Today it's partly-- today it's the second largest city in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But in Hungarian it was called Kassa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "All the trains from Hungary going to Auschwitz went through Kassa.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
